%% Diagram: Decision tree for picking script loading attributes
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart TD
    A[Script to load] --> B{Depends on the DOM<br/>or other scripts?}
    B -->|Yes| C{Order across<br/>scripts matters?}
    B -->|No| D{Modern ESM<br/>entry?}

    C -->|Yes| E[defer]
    C -->|No| F[type=module]

    D -->|Yes| F
    D -->|No| G[async]

    style E fill:#c8e6c9,stroke:#2e7d32
    style F fill:#c8e6c9,stroke:#2e7d32
    style G fill:#bbdefb,stroke:#1565c0
